334
00:23:07,820 --> 00:23:09,456
My sleeping bag!

335
00:23:09,456 --> 00:23:10,690
My blanket!

336
00:23:10,690 --> 00:23:11,958
My teddy bear!

337
00:23:11,958 --> 00:23:14,761
I just need everything,
we're going to the tree!

338
00:23:17,464 --> 00:23:19,231
We're going to the tree.

339
00:23:19,231 --> 00:23:22,001
We're going
to the tree.

