00:23:43,289 --> 00:23:46,325
Haha! Haha!

342
00:23:51,464 --> 00:23:54,333
Come on, Earnest, you
have to be real quiet!

343
00:24:33,239 --> 00:24:37,610
- Do you wanna to read
another letter, sweetie?

344
00:24:42,582 --> 00:24:45,484
- This one Grandpa wrote.

345
00:24:45,484 --> 00:24:47,153
"My Darling Beth,

346
00:24:47,153 --> 00:24:50,389
"I can't believe how long the
days and nights have become.

347
00:24:50,389 --> 00:24:52,091
"I realized there
was a chance that

348
00:24:52,091 --> 00:24:56,062
"we would never hold each other
again and I almost gave up.

349
00:24:56,062 --> 00:24:58,631
"But what kind of man would I
be if I didn't do everything

350
00:24:58,631 --> 00:25:02,468
"humanly possible to be by
your side 'til the day I die?

351
00:25:03,903 --> 00:25:06,573
"I am so pleased
that you are not moving.

352
00:25:06,573 --> 00:25:09,842
"You really have no idea what
that would have done to me.

353
00:25:09,842 --> 00:25:11,477
"Another month has ended
and we are that much

354
00:25:11,477 --> 00:25:14,914
"closer to being in
each others arms.

355
00:25:14,914 --> 00:25:18,150
"I have a busy day tomorrow
and the night is late.

356
00:25:18,150 --> 00:25:20,887
"I look forward to your
next precious letter.

357
00:25:20,887 --> 00:25:22,822
"You are forever in my dreams.

358
00:25:22,822 --> 00:25:25,725
"Your
true love, Will."

359
00:25:27,026 --> 00:25:29,195
- That was really nice, dad.

360
00:25:31,964 --> 00:25:35,201
