369
00:25:49,682 --> 00:25:51,851
- What, who has it easy?

370
00:25:51,851 --> 00:25:53,252
- You do.

371
00:25:53,252 --> 00:25:54,486
- Oh, I have it easy?

372
00:25:54,486 --> 00:25:56,623
- You most certainly do.

373
00:25:56,623 --> 00:25:57,890
- Well, you know what dad?

