00:25:57,890 --> 00:25:59,325
I don't think I do have it easy.

375
00:25:59,325 --> 00:26:01,594
In fact, I think
I have it harder.

376
00:26:01,594 --> 00:26:03,796
- You know what your problem is?

377
00:26:03,796 --> 00:26:05,732
- No, what's my problem?

