wonderful daughters.

380
00:26:12,471 --> 00:26:14,173
- Alright now,
I've heard enough.

381
00:26:14,173 --> 00:26:16,075
First of all,

382
00:26:16,075 --> 00:26:18,645
Fazzle Glue is not stupid.

383
00:26:18,645 --> 00:26:21,013
And secondly, they named
me employee of the year

384
00:26:21,013 --> 00:26:23,082
21 years, straight.

385
00:26:23,082 --> 00:26:25,685
That's an accomplishment, dad!

386
00:26:25,685 --> 00:26:27,687
- I'm done talking to you.

387
00:26:29,722 --> 00:26:30,690
- Well, you know what?

388
00:26:30,690 --> 00:26:31,624
You know what's ridiculous?

389
00:26:31,624 --> 00:26:32,892
I'll tell you what's ridiculous.

390
00:26:32,892 --> 00:26:36,062
You carrying around that
stupid urn all the time.

391
00:26:36,062 --> 00:26:38,698
We can't take you
anywhere with that thing.

392
00:26:43,903 --> 00:26:46,005
Was that Ernest?

393
00:26:47,206 --> 00:26:49,608
Are you kidding me?

394
00:27:12,264 --> 00:27:14,233
Oh my gosh!

395
00:27:21,407 --> 00:27:24,143
- We can't do this
trip with Ernest.

396
00:27:24,143 --> 00:27:26,445
We should turn around.

