00:30:55,054 --> 00:30:56,956
"as I was making
my way here today

424
00:30:56,956 --> 00:30:59,992
"I noticed some men
surveying Jack's property.

425
00:30:59,992 --> 00:31:01,793
"Word around town is
that they are putting

