00:35:02,468 --> 00:35:04,102
- Ernest!

494
00:35:04,102 --> 00:35:08,174
Ernest!

495
00:35:23,322 --> 00:35:25,524
- Alright, go with Mommy.

496
00:35:25,524 --> 00:35:26,925
Come on.

